    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1941-05-10T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1941-05-10T11:00:00-05:00" n="435"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d435">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">851.4016/33: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Germany</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Morris</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1941-05-10T18:00:00+02:00"
                            >May 10, 1941—6 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/> [Received 6:40 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>1829. The DNB<note n="64" xml:id="d435fn64">Deutsches Nachriehten Büro.</note>
                    reports that in discussing the latest measures to exclude Jews from economic
                    life in Paris it was stated by “competent German quarters” there that it is
                    desired to obtain a “uniform settlement of the Jewish question as an
                    international problem” and that <pb facs="0518" n="506" xml:id="pg_506"/> “a
                    final settlement for all Europe will be made with the conclusion of peace”.</p>
                <p>It has been apparent for some time that a systematic plan is being directed from
                    Berlin to establish in all countries under its control the German discrimination
                    against Jews as rapidly as the local situation permits. The first step is in
                    each case exclusion from political activity followed by social ostracism and
                    economic despoliation leading ultimately to compulsory labor, forced emigration
                    and ghettoization.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Morris</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
